Installation
1. If you don't have any software, you can download and buy License of Sketch here:
https://www.sketchapp.com/
Or you can download (FREE) Adobe XD here:
https://www.adobe.com/sea/products/xd.html
2. Installation
With Sketch - Download and Extract the zip ﬁle.
Click To Sketch and Start to use.
You will have 30 days to try before buy Sketch Lisence.
After 30 days, You can buy Sketch Lisence here:
https://www.sketchapp.com/pricing/
With Adobe XD
Download and Open Creative Cloud Desktop App.
Log in to Adobe Creative Cloud with Adobe account or Facebook or Google Account.
Click to Install XD CC
Wait until XD ﬁnish install.
3. Extract File Cahoome.zip
4. Go to Folder Cahoome > Open File Help.PDF or help.html and read the help ﬁle
5. Open ﬁle Cahoome.sketch if you using Sketch Software or Open ﬁle Cahoome.xd
if you using Adobe XD.
6. If you need the turorial about Sketch or Adobe
Go to Sketch Tutorial here: https://www.learnsketch.com/tutorials
Go to Adobe XD Tutorial here: https://helpx.adobe.com/xd/tutorials.html
